description:
good for take out good for eating in
i used to live right upstairs and the staff made take out easy by serving me food on my own kitchen ware {is that weird?}
fake meat is made in house and has a very signature flavor and texture that i myself enjoyed
sauces are flavorful and varied so that you will never get bored of perusing for different menu options
i have gotten food out the door in less than 5 minutes from ordering {vegetarian options are quicker}
